<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>Status is a zero sum game.  Also:<p><i>a perceived threat to one's status activates similar brain networks to a threat to one's life. In the same way, a perceived increase in fairness activates the same reward circuitry as receiving a monetary reward.</i><p><a href="http://www.edbatista.com/2010/03/scarf.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.edbatista.com/2010/03/scarf.html</a></font></span><p><font size=1><font color=#f6f6ef>-----</font></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=120></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_2981029 href="vote?for=2981029&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%75%53%63%4f%31%65%68%56%50%4b"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_2981029></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=specialist">specialist</a> 146 days ago  | <a href="item?id=2981029">link</a></span></div><br>
